	"nodes":[
		{
			"color":"1",
			"height":100,
			"id":"root",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"LLM 从构建到强化学习 深度解析 (Karpathy 2025 教程)",
			"type":"text",
			"width":500,
			"x":0,
			"y":-800
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"intro",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"一、引言：对话界面背后发生了什么？",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":-900,
			"y":-600
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"pretrain",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"二、第一阶段：预训练 (Pre-training)",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":-300,
			"y":-600
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"sft",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"三、第二阶段：监督微调 (SFT)",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":300,
			"y":-600
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"psych",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"四、心理特征：幻觉、工具、推理",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":900,
			"y":-600
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"rlhf",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"五、第三阶段：强化学习与人类反馈 (RLHF)",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":-900,
			"y":-300
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"future",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"六、面向未来：多模态、Agent、在线学习",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":-300,
			"y":-300
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"ecosystem",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"七、模型使用与开源生态",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":300,
			"y":-300
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"summary",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"八、总结：与 ChatGPT 对话本质",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":900,
			"y":-300
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"pretrain_2.1",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"2.1 数据收集与过滤\n- 来源：Common Crawl、The Pile、RefinedWeb\n- 清洗：去噪、去重、去 HTML\n- 过滤：语言、恶意、PII\n- 规模：数 TB ~ 十几 TB",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":-500,
			"y":-450
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"pretrain_2.2",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"2.2 分词 (Tokenization)\n- 方法：BPE 及变种\n- 词表：GPT-4 ~100k\n- 输出：Token ID 序列",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":-300,
			"y":-450
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"pretrain_2.3",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"2.3 自回归训练\n- 任务：预测下一个 Token\n- 模型：Transformer (多层)\n- 损失：交叉熵\n- 成本：算力、分布式、资金\n- 结果：基础模型 (Base Model)",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":-100,
			"y":-450
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"sft_3.1",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"3.1 SFT 必要性\n- Base Model ≠ 对话助手\n- 注入指令/对话风格\n- 安全合规需求",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":200,
			"y":-450
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"sft_3.2",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"3.2 构建对话数据\n- 格式：用户问题 + 理想回答\n- 来源：人工标注 / 模型生成 + 筛选\n- 规模：几十万 ~ 上百万条\n- 含拒答示例",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":350,
			"y":-450
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"sft_3.3",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"3.3 二次自回归训练\n- 格式：<system>、<user>、<assistant>\n- 任务：预测对话中的下一个 Token\n- 结果：初步对话模型",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":500,
			"y":-450
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"psych_4.1",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"4.1 幻觉 (Hallucination)\n- 原因：统计预测无事实区分\n- 缓解：更多上下文 / 强化 '不知道' / 调用工具",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":800,
			"y":-450
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":140,
			"id":"psych_4.2",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"4.2 工具使用 (Tool Use)\n- 搜索引擎 / Python 解释器\n- 触发：特殊 Token 触发系统调用\n- 效果：减少幻觉，提高真实性",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":950,
			"y":-450
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"psych_4.3",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"4.3 多步推理 (CoT)\n- 原因：复杂任务需分解思路\n- 方法：Chain-of-Thought 分步输出\n- 提高：数学/逻辑等准确率",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":1100,
			"y":-450
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"rlhf_5.1",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"5.1 RL 必要性\n- 自主试错探索最优\n- 流程：多方案→评估→强化/惩罚\n- 提升：可验证任务性能",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":-900,
			"y":-150
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"rlhf_5.2",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"5.2 可验证 vs 不可验证\n- 可验证：数学/代码 (标准答案)\n- 不可验证：写作/艺术 (主观)\n- 需：Reward Model",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":-700,
			"y":-150
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"rlhf_5.3",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"5.3 RLHF 局限性\n- 好处：模拟人类偏好\n- 局限：过拟合 Reward 模型漏洞\n- 策略：小步迭代",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":-500,
			"y":-150
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"future_6.1",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"6.1 多模态\n- 文本/图像/音频统一编码\n- 图像Patch/音频频谱Token\n- 应用：多模态 ChatGPT",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":-300,
			"y":-150
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"future_6.2",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"6.2 长程任务与 Agent\n- 多轮 Agent 框架\n- 管理上下文、调用工具、循环迭代",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":-100,
			"y":-150
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"future_6.3",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"6.3 在线学习\n- 推理阶段参数微调\n- 优点：持续进化\n- 风险：安全审计",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":100,
			"y":-150
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"eco_7.1",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"7.1 获取途径\n- 闭源：OpenAI/GPT-4, Claude 等 API\n- 开源：LLaMA, Hugging Face 社区\n- 平台：云服务商、Inference API",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":300,
			"y":-150
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"eco_7.2",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"7.2 Base vs Chat/Instruct\n- Base: 自回归模型\n- Chat/Instruct: 微调对话模型",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":500,
			"y":-150
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"eco_7.3",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"7.3 本地部署\n- 量化(4/8bit) & 蒸馏\n- 硬件：高端 GPU/Apple Silicon",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":700,
			"y":-150
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":140,
			"id":"summary_8.1",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"8.1 系统内部流程\n1. 文本→Token\n2. 上下文+Prompt\n3. 预训练+SFT+RL 自回归生成\n4. 工具调用(可选)\n5. Token→文本",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":900,
			"y":-150
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"summary_8.2",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"8.2 心理比喻\n- SFT: 模仿教师\n- RL: 注入纠错习惯\n- 局限: 学习盲点，不完美",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":1100,
			"y":-150
		}
	]
}